Package: hyper.gam
Type: Package
Title: Generalized Additive Models with Hyper Column
Version: 0.2.3
Description: Generalized additive models with a numeric hyper column.
        Sign-adjustment based on the correlation of model prediction
        and a selected slice of the hyper column. Visualization of the
        integrand surface over the hyper column.
